  "title": "Sales Support Coordinator",
  "description": "<p><br /><strong>Location</strong> : West, 5 day work week<br /><br /><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Support and manage sales activities for overseas customers</li><li>Identify new international business opportunities and markets</li><li>Build and maintain strong relationships with existing and potential overseas customers</li><li>Prepare sales proposals, quotations, and follow up on negotiations with customers</li><li>Coordinate and follow up on sales activities</li><li>Work closely with internal teams to ensure smooth order execution</li><li>Monitor market trends, customer feedback to support sales strategies</li><li>Ensure high levels of customer satisfaction through effective communication and after-sales support</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><p>Diploma or Degree in Business Studies, Business Administration, or a related discipline</p></li><li><p>At least 1 year of relevant experience in international sales and business development. Experience in sales of Automotive products (tyres, rims, and batteries) preferred</p></li><li><p>Strong verbal and written communication skills with excellent interpersonal abilities</p></li><li><p>Proficient in both English and Mandarin to communicate with Mandarin-speaking customers</p></li><li><p>Competent in Microsoft Excel and PowerPoint </p></li><li><p>Demonstrates strong business acumen with good analytical and problem-solving skills</p></li><li><p>Willing to travel overseas</p></li></ul>",
